http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Thiruvananthapuram/358-arrested/article14017133.ece

Consequent upon the police action against goonda and mafia gangs in the State, 358 persons were arrested on January 22.A press note issued here on Friday said 81 persons were arrested in the Thiruvananthapuram range, 39 in Kochi range, 67 in Thrissur range, and 171 in Kannur range. The police action against anti-social elements would be made more stringent in the days to come, the press note added.Nine heldAs many as nine persons have been arrested following 31 raids conducted Statewide against those selling tobacco and tobacco products to schoolchildren. The raids were held from 6 a.m. on January 22 to 6 a.m. on January 23.